but instead of landing in the fountain
it landed in front of my mom.

00:28:36.339 --> 00:28:40.427
So, to celebrate that
my dad made the necklace.

00:28:40.927 --> 00:28:43.680
Wow, that really is a lucky coin.

00:28:44.139 --> 00:28:47.225
That coin is the reason you were born.

00:28:50.979 --> 00:28:54.357
Hana's mom is stupid.

00:28:54.399 --> 00:28:57.986
Stupid, stupid.

