I'm going to head over
after I drop my daughter off.

00:31:58.625 --> 00:32:02.253
No, I have to go change at home.

00:32:02.253 --> 00:32:03.463
Okay, then.

00:32:03.463 --> 00:32:05.798
- See you later.
- Okay, boss's wife.

00:32:13.181 --> 00:32:14.807
Mom, who is that?

00:32:14.807 --> 00:32:17.226
I told you there's a disabled barista
at the café in Dad’s hospital.

00:32:17.226 --> 00:32:18.269
That's her.

00:32:19.562 --> 00:32:22.357
I guess the daughter that she always
brags about goes to Soorim High.

00:32:22.941 --> 00:32:25.360
She said she has
the best grades at school.

00:32:28.404 --> 00:32:31.324
Don't tell me
you lost your spot to her.

00:32:33.201 --> 00:32:36.079
How could you lose
your spot to someone like her?

00:32:36.412 --> 00:32:39.374
What did you say when I told you to go
to a science high school like your sister?

00:32:39.374 --> 00:32:40.625
You said you'd go to a regular school

00:32:40.625 --> 00:32:42.502
get a recommendation from the principal
and get into Seoul National University!

00:32:46.381 --> 00:32:48.257
She's not trying to get into
med school too, is she?

00:32:55.556 --> 00:32:58.601
Hana, you put your hair down today.

00:33:02.939 --> 00:33:04.023
Yeah.

00:33:04.732 --> 00:33:05.942
You're pretty.

00:33:10.321 --> 00:33:12.031
Oh, right.

00:33:12.407 --> 00:33:16.035
This is a charm I bought from a shrine
dedicated to academic success

00:33:16.995 --> 00:33:18.871
and it's supposed to be very effective.

00:33:20.289 --> 00:33:21.833
It's an omamori.

00:33:22.250 --> 00:33:23.584
Thanks.

00:33:24.210 --> 00:33:26.462
Of course you know what it's called.

00:33:30.675 --> 00:33:33.553
Hana, make sure
to get into Seoul University

00:33:34.429 --> 00:33:36.389
and come to Japan to return this to me.

00:33:38.474 --> 00:33:41.310
You need to get rid of it
at the box at Yushima Tenjin.

00:33:41.310 --> 00:33:44.647
If you throw it away anywhere else
the gods will get angry.

00:33:45.314 --> 00:33:47.400
Okay, I will.

