What is it again? Tell me.

00:34:22.268 --> 00:34:24.187
I guess your mom is your boyfriend.

00:34:25.313 --> 00:34:27.356
Did you seize your opportunity and lie

00:34:27.356 --> 00:34:29.108
because you were
embarrassed of being single?

