No, to be exact
she was embarrassed of her mom.

00:34:33.821 --> 00:34:36.449
Her mom's a bit different from others.

00:34:36.657 --> 00:34:38.618
- Na Haeri!
- What?

00:34:39.994 --> 00:34:41.621
You don't like me talking about your mom?

00:34:41.621 --> 00:34:43.539
Is that why you lied
about having a boyfriend?

00:34:44.582 --> 00:34:46.250
Hana didn't lie.

00:34:47.627 --> 00:34:49.378
Hana does have a boyfriend.

00:34:50.213 --> 00:34:52.632
Who is it? Did you see him?

00:34:53.299 --> 00:34:54.509
Yeah.

00:34:56.052 --> 00:34:57.970
I'm her boyfriend.

00:35:01.516 --> 00:35:03.059
Get back to your seats!

00:35:04.435 --> 00:35:05.978
What's with all the commotion?

00:35:09.774 --> 00:35:13.277
A student-teacher will be
observing our class today.

00:35:35.466 --> 00:35:37.426
Does Kang Hana suffer from panic disorder?

00:35:38.553 --> 00:35:40.721
I don't think I've ever
seen her take medicine.

00:35:42.515 --> 00:35:43.850
Hikari.

00:35:44.267 --> 00:35:46.269
Are you really
in a relationship with Hana?

00:35:47.186 --> 00:35:48.771
Why would you ask me that?

00:35:49.147 --> 00:35:51.190
Because you're too good for her.

00:35:51.566 --> 00:35:53.359
Hana has a terrible personality.

00:35:53.693 --> 00:35:56.070
Oh, do you not know what that means?

00:35:57.071 --> 00:36:01.993
You're just too good for her.
Hana only cares about herself.

00:36:01.993 --> 00:36:03.911
Do you get what I'm saying?

