Think about what a tough time
she must've gone through.

00:36:19.760 --> 00:36:21.345
Do you not have a brain?

00:36:21.679 --> 00:36:22.763
Hey.

00:36:23.472 --> 00:36:27.101
Someone who's ashamed of their disabled
mom is the one who should be ashamed!

