I just helped her realize that.

00:36:29.228 --> 00:36:32.106
Yeah! Haeri's right.

00:36:32.106 --> 00:36:35.151
- What are you talking about?
- Why are you shouting?

00:36:35.484 --> 00:36:38.738
- Who are you to say that?
- What's this got to do with you?

00:36:43.701 --> 00:36:45.077
Mom.

00:36:45.369 --> 00:36:48.414
It's not a big deal.
Why are you crying?

00:36:50.499 --> 00:36:53.920
It's vasovagal syncope.

00:36:56.422 --> 00:36:59.675
They said you'll faint again
if you're stressed.

00:36:59.675 --> 00:37:02.595
No, I might.

00:37:04.263 --> 00:37:08.059
It's like a severe case of anemia
so don't worry about it.

00:37:08.643 --> 00:37:13.064
There's not really a cure
and it's not harmful.

00:37:13.439 --> 00:37:14.982
Really?

00:37:15.191 --> 00:37:16.400
Yeah.

00:37:16.692 --> 00:37:19.654
If I feel it coming on

00:37:20.321 --> 00:37:24.033
I just have to lower my head
towards my heart like this.

00:37:24.367 --> 00:37:25.660
Oh...

00:37:26.786 --> 00:37:29.288
Still, you have to rest for a few days.

00:37:29.664 --> 00:37:32.208
You can't go to school to study.

00:37:33.292 --> 00:37:34.543
Yeah.

00:37:35.336 --> 00:37:37.255
I'm not going to go to school.

00:37:39.090 --> 00:37:40.591
Alright.

00:37:41.133 --> 00:37:44.345
Hana will be absent
until she recovers

00:37:44.345 --> 00:37:47.515
- so the vice president needs to step up.
- Okay.

00:37:48.224 --> 00:37:50.476
As for Hikari's guide...

00:37:51.310 --> 00:37:54.188
- Haeri speaks Japanese, so can you help?
- Sure.

00:37:54.647 --> 00:37:57.942
Alright, see you tomorrow.

00:37:58.442 --> 00:38:01.570
- Bye.
- Go right home.

00:38:02.488 --> 00:38:04.824
Hana must be super embarrassed.

00:38:04.824 --> 00:38:06.867
She's not the type
to miss school with finals coming up.

00:38:06.867 --> 00:38:09.578
You don't think
she pretended to faint, do you?

00:38:09.578 --> 00:38:11.998
Wow, if that's the case...

00:38:12.581 --> 00:38:14.583
She deserves an Oscar.

00:38:15.293 --> 00:38:16.544
You two.

00:38:17.295 --> 00:38:18.713
Are you guys really her friends?

